        <h2>Tourist attractions</h2>
        <div class="destinations">
            <h3>Kovalam Beach</h3>
            <p>An internationally renowned beach destination in Kerala offers crescent-shaped shores, cultural programs, Ayurvedic retreats, and nearby attractions like a lighthouse, art galleries, and boating on scenic waters.</p>
     
                
                <img
                 src=
