        <p></p>

        <h2>Food spots</h2>
        <p>Afsal vizhinjam for spicy chicken fry, Rajila hotel for the best mutton dishes, Mothers veg plaza at bakery junction for good sadhya and dosa dishes, Goodmorning and GP hotel for good beef roast and beef fry, Many restos around Vizhinjam and Kovalam for sea food, Asife biriyani. Saranya mess near technopark for early morning Chicken and Mutton Biriyani. Kuravankonam road for many Cafes. Punchakkari Shap for Toddy and many meat dishes like Rabbit, Duck, Pork and variety of sea food. Maha Boli for some Boli and Paayasam(TVM speciality). Try to find good chicken Pakoda, Chicken Thoran ( Available and Shambu Shankaran hotel ). Try many vadas and snacks at tea shops around town. Kumbakonam Filter coffee for some damn good coffee. Malabar Bites ( near Kowdiar) for a variety of snacks.</p>
        
        <p>
            <ul>
                <li><h3>GOOD MORNING HOTEL </h3>
                    <p>
                        For those who appreciate quality food, a warm atmosphere, and attentive service, Good Morning Hotel in Karamana, Thiruvananthapuram is a must-visit destination.
                        the hotel is famous for its flaky porotta and beef curry
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li><h3>PARAGON HOTEL</h3>
                    <p>
                        Paragon Hotel in Trivandrum(keshavadasapuram), Kerala is known for its warm ambiance, high-quality service, and a variety of dining options.
                        The hotel is famous for its soft lagoon chicken biriyani.</p>
                    </p>

                </li>
                <li><h3>MAHA BOLI</h3>
                    <p>
                        For a delicious and authentic palada boli experience in Thiruvananthapuram (Trivandrum), Maha Boli in East Fort, Pazhavangadi is the most famous and popular choice.
                    </p>
                </li>
                     
                
                    
           
